		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_CAMP_NAME"><Text>Precise Layout</Text></Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_CAMP_NAME"><Text>精铺</Text></Row>
		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_CAMP_DESCRIPTION"><Text>Non-capital cities within 6 tiles of your [ICON_Capital] Capital receive +10% to all yields, with an additional +10% for every 10 [ICON_Citizen] Population (max 50%). Non-capital cities more than 6 tiles from your Capital receive -100% to all yields. [ICON_Movement] Settlers receive +1 Movement per turn.</Text></Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LARRY_CAMP_DESCRIPTION"><Text>首都 [ICON_Capital] 6单元格范围内的非首都城市 +10% 全产出，每有10 [ICON_Citizen] 人口再 +10%（最高 +50%）。6格外非首都城市 -100% 全产出。开拓者每回合 +1 [ICON_Movement] 移动力。</Text></Row>

		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_CAMP_NAME"><Text>Camp!</Text></Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_CAMP_NAME"><Text>营地！</Text></Row>
		<Row Language="en_US" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_CAMP_DESCRIPTION"><Text>Camp improvements provide +1 [ICON_Production] Production and +1 [ICON_Gold] Gold. All cities receive +1 [ICON_Food] Food and +1 [ICON_Gold] Gold.</Text></Row>
		<Row Language="zh_Hans_CN" Tag="LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LARRY_CAMP_DESCRIPTION"><Text>营地改良设施 +1 [ICON_Production] 生产力、+1 [ICON_Gold] 金币。所有城市 +1 [ICON_Food] 粮食、+1 [ICON_Gold] 金币。</Text></Row>

